  "detailed_description": "Inside the back rooms of the Toing's Pops candy store in Baltimore, a portal appears. Shining a familiar colour, Bink curiously enters. Through the portal lies an instance of isolation, power, torment, and knowledge. Become empowered, enlightened and isolated to help a particularly knowledgeable friend cheat death.<br><br><strong>MEET THE CEO</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759820/extras/bc5ceeae36117c3190157abf7daf9244.poster.avif?t=1751023624\" width=728 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759820/extras/bc5ceeae36117c3190157abf7daf9244.webm?t=1751023624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759820/extras/bc5ceeae36117c3190157abf7daf9244.mp4?t=1751023624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Meet Chardonnay Hotrod in Toing's Pops 2's Campaign. Chardonnay Hotrod is the CEO of Toing's Pops, and of something else. It goes much deeper than you thought. Learn the horrifying truth, and attempt to stop it.<br><br><strong>BOSS FIGHTS</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759820/extras/67a605c901c07476b75f2d8b70cfc058.poster.avif?t=1751023624\" width=800 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759820/extras/67a605c901c07476b75f2d8b70cfc058.webm?t=1751023624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759820/extras/67a605c901c07476b75f2d8b70cfc058.mp4?t=1751023624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fight your way to Chardonnay, face him, and stop him. But to get to him, you'll have to face someone else first...<br><br><strong>Run, Climb, Slide, and Crawl Your Way to Safety!</strong><br>Toing's Pops 2 introduces new movement to bring a fast pace, and exciting experience to the game. Use these to your advantage in your attempt to save yourself and your friend.",
